rows.label: tlk41700122_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Do you need something? This is
the number one farm in Torigo.

rows.label: tlk41700122_01_msg0002
rows.name:
All the Gulan folk working here
at Kloom Farm are my family.

rows.label: tlk41700122_01_msg0003
rows.name:
We've supported this city's
agriculture for generations.
Since long, long ago.

rows.label: tlk41700122_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Since you've come all this
way, you should take some of
our vegetables with you.
